high_descs: Head straight to reach the living room table.
Pick up the salt shaker from the table.
Turn right to reach the floor lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine the salt shaker under the lamp light.

high_descs: Go to the table straight ahead of you.
Pick up the pepper shaker that is near the long end of the table.
Turn back towards where you started and approach the lamp in the corner of the room.
anns.task_desc: Hold a pepper shaker up to a lamp that is on.

high_descs: Stand up turn around move towards the dining table.
Take the pepper shaker from the dining table.
Turn around move towards the floor lamp.
anns.task_desc: Take the pepper shaker from the dining table and turn on the floor lamp.
